Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂{\rsymbol}…{\r}不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(900,570)}跑起来 吉米!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是指挥室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 请回话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请来人回话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来人{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是{\rsymbol}…{\r}谷田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田军曹 请汇报一下状况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭到敌人炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,附近暂时什么都{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有成功发射照明弹的我们 成了敌人的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告书恐怕会是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请求入木大队长出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地让敌人转移视线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米·哈兹福特在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长 您还平安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者停机了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机师还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不但无法与内部通信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连舱门都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源全部集中到机师保护机能 导致系统关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在等待重启
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能远程操作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西只是接收远程通讯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在必须直接接入银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\rsymbol}…{\r}由我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去银色歼灭者的当机地点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须徒步穿越这片森林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下带您去前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个奇怪的新型机一炮就报销了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没传闻那么强嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入木大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八部队请求我们出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔? 左文字还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就说我们立刻行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前无论如何也要死守前线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说吸引敌人的玩具没了 仍然得按计划给我当诱饵才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁信骑兵大队能所有照明弹全坏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再假咱们也没证据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人兵力正向我们集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那两人帮忙吸引火力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万幸敌人没注意这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦攻击中止 敌人必定进军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个 只能闷声挨远程火炮打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米·哈兹福特正赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骑兵大队已经开始进军
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些混蛋 拿我们当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还剩多少照明弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山並
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有两发备用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就用这个帮大队前进路线照个亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}又不是当兵的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔 惊悚满分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去申请工伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大队的混蛋们得吓一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们队发射了备用照明弹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 这次轮到让他们拖延时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,争取出银色歼灭者重启的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说现在{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在等我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没让他们放照明弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字 这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三骑兵大队交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先别放松神经
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员攻击位置向东移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让敌人盯上银色歼灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿过这里就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点吧 哈兹福特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没启动起来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是有可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我负不起这个责任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还说这个?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说这种话的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对{\rsymbol}…{\r}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回个话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那谁{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越川一等兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这{\rsymbol}…{\r}我找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是越川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击越来越猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说从这边走最快 但外行人没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有别的路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量选条安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少要绕点远
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么束手无策吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会死?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.41,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 装置 唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系统启动流程 运行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辨识密码 0612 0530
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转写 吉米·哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵装扩展 激活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银色歼灭者 全系统启动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即刻起 第八部队开始进军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌方骑兵大队还剩多少兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突入我方阵地的{\rsymbol}…{\r}尚未出现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的曳战者和兵力都派去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能被攻上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.62,0:16:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我队攻来 破坏设施撤退了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少洗个脸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别亏了漂亮脸蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找战后的数据 看能不能学点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不知该怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在银色歼灭者里{\rsymbol}…{\r}关着的那阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次觉得自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果吉米没来 可能真就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实对曳战者一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:19:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 现在也完全没兴趣 将来也没啥自信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.60,0:19:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我只要有个公司能进就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进柯贝尔尼斯工业公司 是因为工资最高
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啥都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括人生目标 憧憬 不满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活得自由自在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 总觉得欠缺什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 会时时觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得再好也会焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为没自信 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能再这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经{\rsymbol}…{\r}走到这一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你{\rsymbol}…{\r}你也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才没看清
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就刚刚的步骤 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是队长的答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与其笨拙地加以束缚 不如让他去自由发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我唐突 你们下一个委派地点定下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚结束作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想让将士们休息无可厚非 但这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照明弹那是事故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括备用弹 全都哑火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是不能有的失误 但战场上常有意外发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在啦在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胜吕先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 我是哈兹福特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你刚才的电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上头听说你肯接手 都非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 特殊补贴也已经发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦 期待你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥特殊补贴{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞一大把钞票就能乐上天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要的数据 看来很快就能收集到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可真不错
